<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Baılyǵym meniń máńgilik</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Baılyǵym meniń máńgilik
 Aıtamyn ony án qylyp.
 Qudaıdan kelgen qýanysh
 Júrekti barady jandyryp

[V2]
 Armanǵa jetken - kóńilim kóktem,
 Ómirime joq meniń ókpem.
 Jaınaǵan kúndeı - aınalam gúldeı
 Qulpyrady baǵym búginde</lyrics>
</song>